        <updateDate>2019-10-29T20:31:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Crossroads of America Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill establishes a pilot program to award grants for freight and highway projects of national or regional significance.</p> <p>The Department of Transportation must give priority to entities that provide the greatest non-federal share of the cost of a project relative to other applications under the pilot program and allot specified percentages of grant funds for small projects and rural projects.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
